HEADWORD: firewheel
<hw>firewheel</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>An annual of the central U. S.
(<spn>Gaillardia pulchella</spn>) having showy long-stalked yellow
flower heads marked with scarlet or purple in the center.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> blanket flower, Indian blanket, <spn>Gaillardia
pulchella</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

